"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1138971","Ministry of Justice","false","2019-07-18","<p>The HMPPS Management Information System was introduced alongside the new education contracts in April this year, and its use is still being embedded across the prison estate. I will write to the Hon Member in Autumn with the information requested once a verified list of courses can be provided, and will place a copy of my letter in the Library.</p>","South Swindon","Robert Buckland",,"2019-07-18T10:42:14.2Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1138971/answer","Biography information for Robert Buckland","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1138971/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1138971/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2019-07-15","Prisoners: Training","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, pursuant to the Answer of 11 July 2019 to Question 273806 on Prisoners: Training, what courses are listed on that HMPPS Management Information System for each prison.","false","Biography information for Richard Burgon","Leeds East","Richard Burgon","277220"
